Mission Orders

The cultists inside the Dark Cathedral are a threat to everything we know.

Hunt {@LinkCreature:25#2011#ossugon warchiefs}, {@LinkCreature:25#2021#ossugon legates}, {@LinkCreature:25#2031#devan deathmasters}, {@LinkCreature:25#2041#Lokian snipers}, {@LinkCreature:25#2042#Lokian blood reapers}, {@LinkCreature:25#2061#devan vanguards}, {@LinkCreature:25#2071#dark deacons}, {@LinkCreature:25#2091#Lokian zealots}, and {@LinkCreature:25#2092#Lokian fanatics}.

Report to Coordinator Delwen when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation. Your guild is an inspiration to all!
